Data download by column names

data_download.Rd

Download columns from supported datasets

data_download(dataset, ...)

Arguments

dataset

a string. Values must be one of the following supported datasets: FRED, WDI, AddHealth, MarsCrater, CtTraffic
...

strings of col_id's found with data_search

Value

A dataframe w/ the input col_id's as columns with the appropriate metadata

Examples

data_download("FRED", "LNU04027659", "G160291A027NBEA")
